You may just be getting to grips with the concept of 3D cinema.

But it appears that technology is already outdated.

Britain’s biggest cinema chain is now preparing to unveil the UK’s first 4DX theatre, which features water sprays, gusts of air, fog and strobe lighting inside the auditorium to simulate the weather and scenes on screen.

