Mooky Greidinger, Cineworld Chief Executive Officer says: ‘We are incredibly excited to be bringing this revolutionary cinematic experience to the UK.

‘Cineworld Milton Keynes will be our first location among many others to come. In 4DX, cinema-goers will become part of the action as sounds, motion, lights and special effects thrill them in their seats.

‘At Cineworld, we are committed to differentiating ourselves – ensuring we are at the forefront of innovation and technology, while giving our customers the most enhanced cinematic experience there is.’

